title: Freaky Friday Flashback: Lizzo Interview/ Donnell Rawlings Interview

description:
This episode we flashed back to your favorite freaky Friday Topics, also we revisit the time Lizzo stopped by for the very first time and spoke about self love, music, and more. Also we flashed back to when Donnell Rawlings stopped by which means the interview was full of jokes and pranks.
